Definition: perennial tropical American vine cultivated for its racemes of showy yellow and purple flowers having the corolla keel coiled like a snail shell
Example: sometimes placed in genus Phaseolus
Synonyms: snail-flower, snail_flower, snail_bean, corkscrew_flower, Vigna_caracalla, Phaseolus_caracalla, legume, genus_Vigna, m, perennial, tropical, American, vine, cultivated, for, its, racemes, of, showy, yellow, and, purple, flowers, having, the, corolla, keel, coiled, like, a, snail, shell, sometimes, placed, in, genus, Phaseolus
Category: noun.plant
